## Architecture (DDD + Layered)

### Layered Architecture

```
src/
├── domain/              # Domain entities, aggregates, value objects, repository interfaces
├── application/         # Services, validators, business logic orchestration
├── presentation/        # Express controllers, HTTP request/response handling
├── infrastructure/      # Logger, Prisma client, technical utilities
├── middleware/          # Express middleware (error handling, logging, etc.)
├── routes/              # Express route definitions
└── index.ts             # Application entry point
```

**Layer Responsibilities**:

| Layer | Responsibility | Examples |
|-------|---|---|
| **Presentation** | HTTP request/response handling | Controllers in `presentation/controllers/` |
| **Application** | Business logic, orchestration | Services in `application/services/`, validation in `application/validator.ts` |
| **Domain** | Core business concepts, invariants | Entities in `domain/models/`, repository interfaces in `domain/repositories/` |
| **Infrastructure** | Technical concerns, Prisma ORM | `infrastructure/logger.ts`, Prisma client setup |

### Data Flow

```
Request
  ↓
Routes → Middleware → Controller
  ↓
Validates input → Service (business logic)
  ↓
Repository interface (domain) → Prisma implementation (infrastructure)
  ↓
Database
  ↓
Response (controller formats DTO)
```

